name: GATENet
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: GATENet Is A GSX Group Initiative And Has A Vision To Build On-Chain Financial Market, Settlement And Registry Solutions To Reduce Costs And Increase Efficiencies For Issuers, Investors And Market Participants Everywhere. GATE Tokens Will Be Used By GATENet For GATENet Fees, Staking, Burning And Governance.
